    "text": "Reviews are written by students to help you decide which minors and courses to take. The reviews are individual opinions of the respective students and are shared only as a basis for your decision. Select a review from the list to read it here. Open full view → ← Back to all Reviews Show department filters Reviews Select a review from the list to preview it here. Filters Department"
